{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6249e93f27","title":"关于打英美军的战术问题","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"289afa2266","index":0,"year":1951,"month":5,"day":29,"articleId":"6249e93f27"}],"tags":[{"id":"625c516d2c","name":"朝鲜战争","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","name":"斯大林选集（诸夏怀斯社2017年5月）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"斯大林，诸夏怀斯社2017年5月","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives5/main/d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"1332d101b8","name":"斯大林"}]},"publication_details":{"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2595661fce","type":"paragraph","text":"关于打英美军的战术问题","index":0,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"6249e93f27"},{"id":"b75f8d6ecc","type":"paragraph","text":"一一致毛泽东电","index":1,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"6249e93f27"},{"id":"59a7d68286","type":"paragraph","text":"（1951年5月29日）","index":2,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"6249e93f27"},{"id":"1c9cd2855d","type":"paragraph","text":"发自莫斯科北京致克拉索夫斯基转毛泽东同志：","index":3,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"6249e93f27"},{"id":"b3bd30be54","type":"paragraph","text":"“我看过了您给彭德怀关于打英美军战术的电报。","index":4,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"6249e93f27"},{"id":"faa9217247","type":"paragraph","text":"该电报中所述计划，我觉得是冒险的。这样计划仅能成功地实施一次或两次","index":5,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"6249e93f27"},{"id":"51e2809c52","type":"paragraph","text":"英美军很容易识破这种计划，从而他们会改变其战术，使你们不可能每次都不受损失地把敌主力引到北面。","index":6,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"6249e93f27"},{"id":"af406b180d","type":"paragraph","text":"如果你们在前线后方有构筑很好的防御工事，能迅速将故主力吸引到这单，那么在这种条件下倒不奶再冒险试一试，采用这一计划。然而，据我所知，你们目前在朝鲜尚无这样的工事。因此，这里的危险性就在于，英美军一且识破了你们的计划，就不会给你们以实施机动的可能性。而由于你们是第四次重复这一计划，那也就很容易被英美军识破。","index":7,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"6249e93f27"},{"id":"8db90b9ed1","type":"paragraph","text":"此外，还应考虑到，英美军向北推进时，将一道接一道地建立起新的防线，从而使你们在一且需要实施进攻时，难以不付出巨大损失就能突破英美军防线。这当然是我们不愿意看到的。拿将介石军队作类比，这也是不能令人信服的，因为：第一，你们现在所对付的是不同的军队：第二，还没有任何根据可以认为，英美军会像落介石那样惠鑫，使你们能够按照你们的选择每次外灭故1个整营地外灭其军队","index":8,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"6249e93f27"},{"id":"1696ee89c5","type":"paragraph","text":"还应注意到，如果平再次落入敌人手里，这一方面会降低朝鲜人民和朝鲜军队的士气，另一方面将提高英美军队的士气。","index":9,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"6249e93f27"},{"id":"f33e592d8d","type":"paragraph","text":"看来你们将要准备一次重大的战役，其日的当然不是为了局部机动，而是为了给英美车以沉重打击","index":10,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"6249e93f27"},{"id":"409ac9400c","type":"paragraph","text":"菲利波夫","index":11,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"6249e93f27"},{"id":"4ad8f95be6","type":"paragraph","text":"第284号密码电报","index":12,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"6249e93f27"},{"id":"6218e15d94","type":"paragraph","text":"1951年5月29日《朝鲜战争：俄国档案馆的解密文件》","index":13,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"6249e93f27"},{"id":"8e5913623c","type":"paragraph","text":"选自新编《斯大林全集》（中册）第774页","index":14,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"6249e93f27"},{"id":"bef588e481","type":"paragraph","text":"档案附卷九第130—131页","index":15,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"6249e93f27"}],"page":{"id":"92f932f9ba","publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"6249e93f27","start":2747,"end":2748}}}},"__N_SSG":true}